title: Looking Forward to Warhammer Preview Online – AdeptiCon 2023
description: We're off to Chicago! We'll have all the big news and more from this year's AdeptiCon. https://bit.ly/3J51YKU

title: Hedonites of Slaanesh: Lord of Hubris in 10 Paints
description:
Utterly enamoured with their own magnificence, the strutting peacocks known as Lords of Hubris swagger into battle. Follow this step-by-step guide to paint your Lord of Hubris quickly and effectively with just 10 paints.

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6

Don't forget to like, share and subscribe and to ring the bell to make sure you keep up to date with all our latest videos!
